        .col-2
            .logo.dropfade
            h1.title.brand
                .dropfade David Leger
            span.breakline.fade.ani-long
            h2.tagline.risefade.ani-long Hey! My name's 
                span.bigger.pink David
                | . <br />I like to 
                span.bigger.green design 
                | things, and 
                span.bigger.purple code 
                | stuff!
            .next-button.btn-me.fade.ani-long